And
GOVERNMENT
Of the
TURKS.</P>
<P>Together with
A Survey of the SEVEN
CHURCHES OF ASIA,
As they now lye in their Ruines:
AND
A Brief De&s;cription of
CONSTANTINOPLE.</P>
<P>By <HI>Tho. Smith,</HI> B. D. and Fellow of
St. <HI>Mary Magdalen</HI> College <HI>Oxon.</HI></P>
<P><HI>London,</HI> Printed for <HI>Mo&s;es Pitt,</HI> at the Angel in
St. <HI>Pauls</HI> Church-yard, M.DC.LXX.VIII.</P>
</DIV1>
