<P>On the &s;ide of a large &s;tone-coffin
in form of a che&s;t, the cover taken
off, in the middle of a Court of a
Seraglio, is the following in&s;cription
of &s;ix very long lines, the letters en|graven
&s;mall, and very clo&s;e; where
there is mention made twice of the
City of the <HI>Thyatirenians.</HI></P>
